title: Ananda's Vegetarian Restaurant
description: Specialties include silken tofu with shimeji mushroom sauce, tomyam fried rice, stir fried chicken with chili (very spicy). Has buffet every 1st and 15th day of lunar calendar (better check with the restaurant first to confirm the date). Also sells vegetarian goods. Has Wi-Fi.
streetAddress: Jl Pluit Karang Timur Blok O-8 no. 57-58, Muara Karang
